Add Image Column in Database

Add a column in your table (for example users table).

Example migration:

$table->string('image')->nullable();

If table already exists run migration:

php artisan make:migration add_image_to_users_table

Then inside migration:

Schema::table('users', function (Blueprint $table) {
    $table->string('image')->nullable();
});

Run:

php artisan migrate
2️⃣ Add Image Upload in Form

